{"tid":1612631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一招擊退搜身","createTime":"2019-10-02T10:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T10:40:48.000Z","uid":172158,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"607fffb2d5b8f469ab574e3f84509e02251aa27b","tid":1612631,"uid":172158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:05:21.000Z","msg":"我個朋友講，頭先有狗想搜佢身，問佢個背囊做乜咁脹，有啲咩喺裏面。 我個friend就話: 冇嘢嘅冇嘢嘅&hellip;&hellip;裏面淨係有啲私人物品啫&hellip;&hellip;隻狗就話: 係咩嚟嘅，打開嚟睇！跟住我個friend就繼續口窒窒咁話: 嗰啲嘢攞嚟索血㗎咋，真係冇嘢㗎&hellip;&hellip;跟住隻狗已經忍唔住即刻一手搶咗佢個袋，打開咗。結果佢停咗兩秒之後就話: 咩料呀！做乜帶住兩大pack m巾周圍走？！我個friend就話: 而家唔係幫女朋友買m巾都唔得吖嘛，我已經好慘㗎喇！畀條生路嚟行好喎！"},{"pid":"ee1aa9f3f88536de6b7fa628af7bb6f57546ee39","tid":1612631,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:06:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fec09ef9deea48389e295dd49797188dc579b54f","tid":1612631,"uid":186142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:09:19.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻阻你<br />\n唔好再指責所謂偽勇武 入嚟睇下小勇武點可以有大作為<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【實際行動戰術整合】正式宣佈下回合開始將會冇人被捕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1611678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1611678</a>"},{"pid":"d102ba3d08a0caed77a4042ba30f2d355e521379","tid":1612631,"uid":254594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:10:07.000Z","msg":"玩狗定玩自己？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce85e7731af4c7adfee9179a08da55a8a6c2a431","tid":1612631,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:11:15.000Z","msg":"樓豬不如講白d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2937753d102415424adfbce7943d71ef85ddc5c8","tid":1612631,"uid":172568,"like":0,"dislike